OL,5, Parcel delivery firms are failing to   
OL,6, deliver on customer satisfaction,      
OL,7, according to a league table.           
OL,9,FHermes and Yodel came bottom in a      
OL,10,Fsurvey by Citizens Advice (CA) and     
OL,11,FAmazon Logistics was top, but all the  
OL,12,Ffirms had performance issues.          
OL,14,FThe report, ahead of the busy Christmas
OL,15,Fperiod, compared several criteria,     
OL,16,Fincluding customer service and trust.  
OL,18,FDelivery firms were a lifeline for many
OL,19,Fpeople during lockdown but there are   
OL,20,F"huge cracks" in the sector, CA said.  
